# lore_savage_npc_token [9004]
#
You discover an ancient, worn, leather and bone horn, crudely
fashioned.  Upon raising it to your lips, you sense the presence
of several bands of savages nearby.  You find these units will
respond to your mental control, and you can issue the following
commands to your savage units:

   ADMIT, ATTACK, BANNER, BEHIND, CONTACT, DEFAULT, DEFEND, DROP,
   EXECUTE, FLAG, GIVE, HOSTILE, MOVE, NAME, NEUTRAL, PILLAGE,
   PROMOTE, RAZE, SEEK, STACK, STOP, TAKE, TERRORIZE, UNSTACK, WAIT
